Closes https://github.com/metabase/metabase/issues/45286

### Description

Allows SDK users to pass their own function to refresh the authentication token. This allows them to specify their own implementation of querying the refresh token, such as for token-based authentication (as opposed to session-based)

```ts
// This is our default implementation.
async function fetchRefreshToken(url: string) {
  const response = await fetch(url, {
    method: "GET",
    credentials: "include",
  });

  return await response.json();
}

const config = { fetchRefreshToken }
```

