Adds the overflow menu to the `Interactive Dashboard` and provides two main ways to customize the menu via plugins:
- Adding your own menu component with `plugins.dashboard.dashcardMenu = ReactNode`
- Adding custom menu items and removing default items with 
```
plugins.dashboard.dashcardMenu = {
  withDownloads?: boolean;
  withEditLink?: boolean;
  customItems?: (
    | DashCardMenuItem
    | (({ question }: { question?: Question }) => DashCardMenuItem)
  )[];
};
```

`customItems` also allows users to add their own menu items, while having the ability to use the inner question's data if they choose to.
